.TH pif-tags 1  "pif-tags " 
.SH NAME
pif\-tags \- List all available tags
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBpif\-tags\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
List all available tags
.PP
Prints every tag that appears across the registry. Tags are short category labels (e.g. "library", "parser", "graphics") attached to individual extensions.
.PP
Use a tag as a filter with \-\-tag in the list, search, or info commands to narrow results to a specific category.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
